##### Investment Analyst / Manager, Family Office

A family office in Hong Kong, Dragon Bridge (Holdings) Limited, is looking for an Investment Analyst/Manager who has strong expertise and skills preferably in Commodities/ Healthcare/ Technology to join their dynamic investment team.

**Main functions:**

• Originate investment ideas, preferably in respect of Commodities/ Healthcare/ Technology in global equities and bond market;

• Provide insights on the upcoming economic and industry trends, with deep awareness of macro events and economy;

• Perform advance financial modeling in Excel and familiar with valuation methodologies, including but not limited to SOTP, DCF and CCA analysis.  Statistical modeling is a plus;

• Candidates with more extensive experience will be considered for manager position.

**Requirements:**

• University graduate with at least 5 to 7 years experience ;

• Able to work independently and under pressure;

• Deep understanding and knowledge of the financial markets;

• Proficient in Bloomberg, Excel, PowerPoint and other relevant tools;

• Excellent analytical skills with good judgement, able to generate investment ideas with strong quantitative and qualitative supporting materials to back up the stand;

• Good master of macro and industry analysis;

• Excellent written and oral English, Cantonese, Mandarin;

• Enjoy working in a small team environment;

